{"tid":149930,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「字海」我個胃好痛，我戀愛了嗎？","createTime":"2017-03-09T15:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T07:10:59.000Z","uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"136ec91cfd62632c0812a0378bce5a7403420223","tid":149930,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"嘴上雖然說著愛呀喜歡啊什麼的，而真心卻隱藏於迷霧之中，都是一樣蒼白空虛，都頭來，謊言被戳穿，心願未了。<br />\n就算如此我也沒有後悔過，雖說一開始是故意為之，但單相思的那份心跳，失戀時的心痛，我都能夠這樣真切地感受過了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63Hyvo8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63Hyvo8.jpg&h=21bc6421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母我睇撚到好唔開心，想喊，我感同身受，單戀真係好慘，仲要支持佢地，幫佢講好說話...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛你呀，就算你有男朋友，我都會咁愛你，我會足你第11年嫁，都等左10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧子 : 「我..想談一次戀愛」<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣佈&quot;藤之宮寧子&quot;係女神，我愛你！<br />\n小鳥絲請你立即道歉，唔好再懷疑佢係雞，你好撚侮辱佢!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個咁純咁乖既女仔，身體有事，仲要比MK仔玩弄，搞到訓醫院屌你老母!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「你要這樣下去，和我走一樣的路嗎?要和我落同一個下場嗎?」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/09/233551_ca1805a49bb73d0437c2004b8b9ba8b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F233551_ca1805a49bb73d0437c2004b8b9ba8b1.jpg&h=a21a9c83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c6fdf4e483c3b603bbd9bcbea299d80ad251915","tid":149930,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ufqnVI8qQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-ufqnVI8qQQ&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=42319120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ufqnVI8qQQ</a>"},{"pid":"5e5d98f5f6b7c06ea7087350eadd1c3d17b73498","tid":149930,"uid":5